gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2
Interface Model.AddSubject

All Known Subinterfaces:
Model.AddContext
Enclosing interface:
Model
public static interface Model.AddSubject

A builder of a triple addition, which allows the user to define the subject of the to-be-added triple.
